      "errorPath": "and-or-event-confusion",
      "statement": "任何兩事件都可用P(A或B)=P(A)+P(B)，不需扣除重疊。",
      "correctAnswer": false,
      "explanation": "一般公式為P(A∪B)=P(A)+P(B)−P(A∩B)。"
